::Kaiser::
       "Indeed, our winged friend is correct.  The Predacons are retreating, 
although not without dealing some damage.  The Tripred ship is gone, as are 
the renegade preds.  I don't detect any other fatalities.  But I may be 
wrong."  He shrugs and turns back to his analysis.
